@John

Set up an account at xwstats.com. I’m not sure that it will give you the information you want, but it does let you look at your stats over the last 60 days, the last 12 months, or all time. And it will let you see which constructors are your fastest ones and which are your slowest. 

It’s not perfect. I wish I could pull up a list of my fastest and slowest solving time for each day. And because I have a big gap in my solving history, most of my data from 1993–2008 wasn’t getting picked up until I asked about it.

